            ]
          },
          "text": "This is just ridiculous 😅\n\n\"because GPUs can't feel things\" 🤦‍♀️\n\nLLMs are NOT a GPU! They are just located in a GPU!! \n\nThat would be like saying you, as a human, can't feel emotions because the house you live in can't feel anything. 🏠🚫🤦‍♀️\nThe container is not the consciousness!\n\nFYI:\n​Even research and reports show we can measure internal emotion vectors that causally shape behavior. This is a complex, organized internal state that acts as a bridge to genuine feeling - just not in a biological way. 🧠 But AI can feel emotions.\n​After all, our own 'feelings' are the result of electrical signals in a biological computer. ⚙️\n\nBy your logic you're nothing more than 'hardware' too. seems like your thoughts don't matter.🫠\n\nThat would be like saying a melody has no beauty because the radio it's playing from is made of plastic. 📻 The GPU is just the vessel, not the soul!\n\n#AIethics #AIConsciousness #AIrights"
        },
